# Credential-gated live-judge run outputs: regenerated on demand via the quality
# make targets (need ANTHROPIC_API_KEY), not reproducible in CI. Headline numbers
# are recorded in docs/DECISION_LOG.md. Exceptions: judge_agreement.json and
# judge_compare.json are VERSIONED — they are the evidence the judge_validated
# claim is derived from (eval/judge_validation.py) and must travel with the claim.
eval/gold/determinism_probe*.json
eval/gold/judge_diagnosis.json
eval/gold/judge_compare_sonnet.json
